# NOTE on the ONNX model file
# aria_policy.onnx is intentionally NOT ignored -- it's a small
# (~14.5KB) verified export and is expected to be committed so the
# project runs out of the box. If your model grows large in a future
# retrain, consider Git LFS instead of excluding it outright.

